"use strict";(self.webpackChunkFirmament=self.webpackChunkFirmament||[]).push([[1477],{30010:e=>{e.exports=JSON.parse('{"blogPosts":[{"id":"Gomoku","metadata":{"permalink":"/blog/Gomoku","source":"@site/blog/2023-03-03-gomoku/index.md","title":"Gomoku","description":"This week we modified tic-tac-toe game and implemented Gomoku (5-in-a-row game). We used fontawesome for SVG icons.","date":"2023-03-03T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"March 3, 2023","tags":[{"label":"apps","permalink":"/blog/tags/apps"},{"label":"games","permalink":"/blog/tags/games"},{"label":"gomoku","permalink":"/blog/tags/gomoku"},{"label":"5-in-a-row","permalink":"/blog/tags/5-in-a-row"}],"readingTime":0.225,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[{"name":"Po","title":"Freelancer","url":"https://github.com/piratepo","imageURL":"https://github.com/piratepo.png","key":"po"},{"name":"Sing Chun","title":"Freelancer","url":"https://github.com/singchun","imageURL":"https://github.com/singchun.png","key":"singchun"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"Gomoku","title":"Gomoku","authors":["po","singchun"],"tags":["apps","games","gomoku","5-in-a-row"]},"nextItem":{"title":"Sentiment News and Tic-tac-toe","permalink":"/blog/sentiment-news-and-tic-tac-toe"}},"content":"This week we modified [tic-tac-toe game](/docs/TicTacToe) and implemented [Gomoku](/docs/Gomoku) (5-in-a-row game). We used [fontawesome](https://fontawesome.com/v6/docs/web/use-with/react/) for SVG icons.\\r\\n\\r\\n\u4eca\u500b\u79ae\u62dc\u6211\u54cb\u6539\u5de6[\u4e95\u5b57\u904e\u4e09\u95dc](/docs/TicTacToe)\u5beb\u5497\u96bb[\u4e94\u5b50\u68cb](/docs/Gomoku)\u3002\u6211\u54cb\u7528\u5497[fontawesome](https://fontawesome.com/v6/docs/web/use-with/react/)\u505aicons\u3002"},{"id":"sentiment-news-and-tic-tac-toe","metadata":{"permalink":"/blog/sentiment-news-and-tic-tac-toe","source":"@site/blog/2023-02-24-sentiment-news-and-tic-tac-toe/index.md","title":"Sentiment News and Tic-tac-toe","description":"We used SnowNLP and pysenti to compute two sentiment scores for each HK news that we scrapped daily. Using these scores, we visualize the news in a sentiment square. From this visualization, we can roughly know how happy/sad daily HK news is. On the other hand, we started our game development journal. Inspired by the simple tic-tac-toe implementation by Fellipe Utakausing tailwind and react, we implemented similarly our own tic-tac-toe game.","date":"2023-02-24T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"February 24, 2023","tags":[{"label":"apps","permalink":"/blog/tags/apps"},{"label":"news","permalink":"/blog/tags/news"},{"label":"sentiment","permalink":"/blog/tags/sentiment"},{"label":"tic-tac-toe","permalink":"/blog/tags/tic-tac-toe"}],"readingTime":0.985,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[{"name":"Po","title":"Freelancer","url":"https://github.com/piratepo","imageURL":"https://github.com/piratepo.png","key":"po"},{"name":"Sing Chun","title":"Freelancer","url":"https://github.com/singchun","imageURL":"https://github.com/singchun.png","key":"singchun"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"sentiment-news-and-tic-tac-toe","title":"Sentiment News and Tic-tac-toe","authors":["po","singchun"],"tags":["apps","news","sentiment","tic-tac-toe"]},"prevItem":{"title":"Gomoku","permalink":"/blog/Gomoku"},"nextItem":{"title":"HK News on a Sphere","permalink":"/blog/news-on-sphere"}},"content":"We used [SnowNLP](https://pypi.org/project/snownlp/) and [pysenti](https://pypi.org/project/pysenti/) to compute two sentiment scores for each HK news that we scrapped daily. Using these scores, we visualize the news in a [sentiment square](/docs/SentimentNews). From this visualization, we can roughly know how happy/sad daily HK news is. On the other hand, we started our game development journal. Inspired by the simple tic-tac-toe implementation by [Fellipe Utaka](https://reactjsexample.com/a-tic-tac-toe-game-made-with-react-and-tailwind-css/)using tailwind and react, we implemented similarly our own [tic-tac-toe game](/docs/TicTacToe).\\r\\n\\r\\n\u6211\u54cb\u7528\u5497[SnowNLP](https://pypi.org/project/snownlp/)\u540c[pysenti](https://pypi.org/project/pysenti/)\u53bb\u8a08\u6bcf\u55ae\u9999\u6e2f\u6bcf\u65e5\u65b0\u805e\u5605\u60c5\u611f\u5206\u6578\uff0c\u7136\u5f8c\u7528\u5462\u5169\u500b\u60c5\u611f\u5206\u6578\u5c07\u65b0\u805e\u986f\u793a\u4fc2\u4e00\u500b[\u4e8c\u7dad\u60c5\u611f\u5e73\u9762](/docs/SentimentNews)\u4e0a\u3002\u901a\u904e\u5462\u500b\u986f\u793a\u65b9\u6cd5\uff0c\u6211\u54cb\u53ef\u4ee5\u5927\u6982\u898b\u5230\u9999\u6e2f\u6bcf\u65e5\u65b0\u805e\u4fc2\u958b\u5fc3\u591a\u5b9a\u4fc2\u50b7\u5fc3\u591a\u3002\u6b64\u5916\uff0c\u6211\u54cb\u4ea6\u8e0f\u4e0a\u5beb\u904a\u6232\u5605\u65c5\u7a0b\u3002\u7747\u5230[Fellipe Utaka](https://reactjsexample.com/a-tic-tac-toe-game-made-with-react-and-tailwind-css/)\u7c21\u55ae\u5730\u7528tailwind\u540creact\u53bb\u5beb\u4e95\u5b57\u904e\u4e09\u95dc\uff0c\u6211\u54cb\u90fd\u5beb\u5de6\u4e00\u500b\u76f8\u4f3c\u5605[\u4e95\u5b57\u904e\u4e09\u95dc](/docs/TicTacToe)\u3002"},{"id":"news-on-sphere","metadata":{"permalink":"/blog/news-on-sphere","source":"@site/blog/2023-02-10-news-on-sphere/index.md","title":"HK News on a Sphere","description":"We added a cronjob on our server to scrape HK news daily and store them on FireStore. Then we implemented a query to search for the news and used the technique demonstrated by raizensoft (video here) to display HK news on a sphere. To display arbitrary numbers of news evenly on the sphere, we used spherical Fibonacci mapping.","date":"2023-02-10T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"February 10, 2023","tags":[{"label":"apps","permalink":"/blog/tags/apps"},{"label":"news","permalink":"/blog/tags/news"},{"label":"search","permalink":"/blog/tags/search"},{"label":"database","permalink":"/blog/tags/database"},{"label":"cronjob","permalink":"/blog/tags/cronjob"},{"label":"sphere","permalink":"/blog/tags/sphere"}],"readingTime":0.735,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[{"name":"Po","title":"Freelancer","url":"https://github.com/piratepo","imageURL":"https://github.com/piratepo.png","key":"po"},{"name":"Sing Chun","title":"Freelancer","url":"https://github.com/singchun","imageURL":"https://github.com/singchun.png","key":"singchun"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"news-on-sphere","title":"HK News on a Sphere","authors":["po","singchun"],"tags":["apps","news","search","database","cronjob","sphere"]},"prevItem":{"title":"Sentiment News and Tic-tac-toe","permalink":"/blog/sentiment-news-and-tic-tac-toe"},"nextItem":{"title":"HK News Scraper","permalink":"/blog/news-scraper"}},"content":"We added a cronjob on our server to scrape HK news daily and store them on FireStore. Then we implemented a query to [search for the news](/docs/SearchNews) and used the technique demonstrated by [raizensoft](https://www.youtube.com/@raizensoft) (video [here](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xqpUsk3HWic)) to display HK [news on a sphere](/docs/SphereNews). To display arbitrary numbers of news evenly on the sphere, we used [spherical Fibonacci mapping](https://doi.org/10.1145/2816795.2818131).\\r\\n\\r\\n\u6211\u54cb\u52a0\u5497\u500bcornjob\u4fc2server\u4e0a\u6bcf\u65e5\u722c\u9999\u6e2f\u65b0\u805e\u540c\u5132\u5b58\u4fc2FireStore\u4e0a\u9762\u3002\u7136\u5f8c\u6211\u54cb\u5beb\u5497\u500bquery\u53bb[\u6435\u9999\u6e2f\u65b0\u9592](/docs/SearchNews)\u540c\u7528\u5497[raizensoft](https://www.youtube.com/@raizensoft)\u4fc2[\u5462\u55a5](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xqpUsk3HWic)\u793a\u7bc4\u5605\u6280\u5de7\u5c07\u6bcf\u65e5\u5605[\u9999\u6e2f\u65b0\u9592\u986f\u793a\u4fc2\u7403\u4e0a\u9762](/docs/SphereNews)\u3002\u6211\u54cb\u7528\u5497[spherical Fibonacci mapping](https://doi.org/10.1145/2816795.2818131)\u5c07\u4efb\u610f\u6578\u76ee\u5605\u65b0\u9592\u5e73\u5747\u5730\u653e\u4fc2\u7403\u4e0a\u9762\u3002"},{"id":"news-scraper","metadata":{"permalink":"/blog/news-scraper","source":"@site/blog/2023-01-14-news-scraper/index.md","title":"HK News Scraper","description":"We scrapped HK news using CORS proxy and cheerio to feed live news from below news channels:","date":"2023-01-14T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"January 14, 2023","tags":[{"label":"apps","permalink":"/blog/tags/apps"},{"label":"news","permalink":"/blog/tags/news"},{"label":"scaper","permalink":"/blog/tags/scaper"}],"readingTime":0.92,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[{"name":"Po","title":"Freelancer","url":"https://github.com/piratepo","imageURL":"https://github.com/piratepo.png","key":"po"},{"name":"Sing Chun","title":"Freelancer","url":"https://github.com/singchun","imageURL":"https://github.com/singchun.png","key":"singchun"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"news-scraper","title":"HK News Scraper","authors":["po","singchun"],"tags":["apps","news","scaper"]},"prevItem":{"title":"HK News on a Sphere","permalink":"/blog/news-on-sphere"},"nextItem":{"title":"First Realtime Database Apps","permalink":"/blog/first-apps"}},"content":"We scrapped HK news using [CORS proxy](https://cors-anywhere.herokuapp.com/) and [cheerio](https://cheerio.js.org/) to feed live news from below news channels:\\r\\n\\r\\n\u6211\u54cb\u7528\u5497[CORS proxy](https://cors-anywhere.herokuapp.com/)\u540c[cheerio](https://cheerio.js.org/)\u53bb\u6536\u96c6\u4e0b\u9762\u5404\u65b0\u805e\u7db2\u5605\u5373\u6642/\u7126\u9ede\u65b0\u9592\uff1a\\r\\n\\r\\n- [HK01/\u9999\u6e2f01](https://www.hk01.com)\\r\\n- [Ta Kung Pao/\u5927\u516c\u5831](http://www.takungpao.com.hk)\\r\\n- [Sing Tao Daily/\u661f\u5cf6\u65e5\u5831](https://www.stheadline.com)\\r\\n- [Oriental Daily News/\u6771\u65b9\u65e5\u5831](https://hk.on.cc)\\r\\n- [Ming Pao/\u660e\u5831](https://news.mingpao.com/pns)\\r\\n- [Vision Times/\u770b\u4e2d\u570b](https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/index.html)\\r\\n- [Epoch Times/\u5927\u7d00\u5143](https://www.epochtimes.com/b5)\\r\\n- [Yahoo/\u96c5\u864e](https://hk.news.yahoo.com)\\r\\n- [HKCNA/\u9999\u6e2f\u65b0\u9592\u7db2](http://www.hkcna.hk)\\r\\n- [RTHK News/\u9999\u6e2f\u96fb\u53f0](https://news.rthk.hk)\\r\\n- [HK Matters/\u9999\u6e2f\u65b0\u805e\u9023\u7dda](https://news.hongkongmetas.com)\\r\\n- [TVB News/\u7121\u7dda\u65b0\u805e](https://news.tvb.com/tc)\\r\\n- [Gov News/\u653f\u5e9c\u65b0\u805e\u7db2](https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/index.html)\\r\\n- [Wen Wei Po/\u6587\u532f\u5831](https://www.wenweipo.com/immed/hongkong)\\r\\n- [am730](https://www.am730.com.hk)\\r\\n- [Now News/Now \u65b0\u805e](https://news.now.com/home)\\r\\n- [BBC News/BBC \u65b0\u805e](https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad)\\r\\n- [ABC News/ABC \u65b0\u805e](https://www.abc.net.au/news/chinese/china)\\r\\n- [CBC Radio/\u52a0\u62ff\u5927\u65b0\u805e](https://ici.radio-canada.ca/rci/zh-hant)\\r\\n- [NY Times/\u7d10\u7d04\u6642\u5831](https://cn.nytimes.com/hk-taiwan/zh-hant/)"},{"id":"first-apps","metadata":{"permalink":"/blog/first-apps","source":"@site/blog/2022-12-26-first-apps/index.md","title":"First Realtime Database Apps","description":"We customized a navbar item (with this workaround) for \\"menu bar log-in\\" using Firebase Authentication and wrote two simple apps to read/write data to/from Firebase Realtime Database.","date":"2022-12-26T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"December 26, 2022","tags":[{"label":"first","permalink":"/blog/tags/first"},{"label":"apps","permalink":"/blog/tags/apps"}],"readingTime":0.335,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[{"name":"Po","title":"Freelancer","url":"https://github.com/piratepo","imageURL":"https://github.com/piratepo.png","key":"po"},{"name":"Sing Chun","title":"Freelancer","url":"https://github.com/singchun","imageURL":"https://github.com/singchun.png","key":"singchun"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"first-apps","title":"First Realtime Database Apps","authors":["po","singchun"],"tags":["first","apps"]},"prevItem":{"title":"HK News Scraper","permalink":"/blog/news-scraper"},"nextItem":{"title":"Welcome","permalink":"/blog/welcome"}},"content":"We customized a navbar item (with this [workaround](https://github.com/facebook/docusaurus/pull/7231)) for \\"menu bar log-in\\" using [Firebase Authentication](https://firebase.google.com/docs/auth?hl=en) and wrote two simple apps to read/write data to/from [Firebase Realtime Database](https://firebase.google.com/docs/database?hl=en).\\r\\n\\r\\n\u7528\u5497[\u5462\u55f0post](https://github.com/facebook/docusaurus/pull/7231)\u6559\u5605workaround\u6574\u5497\u7528[Firebase Authentication](https://firebase.google.com/docs/auth?hl=en)\u5605\\"menu bar log-in\\"\uff0c\u540c\u57cb\u5beb\u5497\u5169\u500b\u7c21\u55ae\u5605[Firebase Realtime Database](https://firebase.google.com/docs/database?hl=en)\u8b80\u5165\u5beb\u51fa\u5605web apps\u3002\\r\\n\\r\\n- [Read](/docs/Display)\\r\\n- [Write](/docs/Submit)"},{"id":"welcome","metadata":{"permalink":"/blog/welcome","source":"@site/blog/2022-12-20-welcome/index.md","title":"Welcome","description":"Today, we established our home website for hosting to-be-developed fun web apps! We used Docusaurus.","date":"2022-12-20T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"December 20, 2022","tags":[{"label":"hello","permalink":"/blog/tags/hello"}],"readingTime":0.195,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[{"name":"Po","title":"Freelancer","url":"https://github.com/piratepo","imageURL":"https://github.com/piratepo.png","key":"po"},{"name":"Sing Chun","title":"Freelancer","url":"https://github.com/singchun","imageURL":"https://github.com/singchun.png","key":"singchun"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"welcome","title":"Welcome","authors":["po","singchun"],"tags":["hello"]},"prevItem":{"title":"First Realtime Database Apps","permalink":"/blog/first-apps"}},"content":"Today, we established our home website for hosting to-be-developed fun web apps! We used [Docusaurus](https://docusaurus.io/).\\r\\n\\r\\n\u4eca\u65e5\uff0c\u6211\u54cb\u8d77\u5497\u5462\u55f0\u7db2\u9801\u7528\u65bc\u958b\u767c\u6709\u8da3\u5605web apps\uff01\u6211\u54cb\u7528\u5497[Docusaurus](https://docusaurus.io/)."}]}')}}]);